c.poster.avif?t=1774025111\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374230/extras/74c0a0d4730736adb543e843b39bd41c.webm?t=1774025111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374230/extras/74c0a0d4730736adb543e843b39bd41c.mp4?t=1774025111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374230/extras/ec11684dd93cf2a5c8849bccfe3aa053.avif?t=1774025111\" width=616 height=76 /></span>At the start of each level lies Vulpis Village. The Vulpis are friends to a brave charcoal like yourself, so they're happy to provide a service. Here you can rest, enhance abilities, rebuild and upgrade structures thanks to the resources you collect. The village changes along with your progress and opens up all-new gameplay features each time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374230/extras/ea18867ced3564bf778e49abfe273b6f.poster.avif?t=1774025111\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374230/extras/ea18867ced3564bf778e49abfe273b6f.webm?t=1774025111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374230/extras/ea18867ced3564bf778e49abfe273b6f.mp4?t=1774025111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
